<a id="integrity"></a>

> [!WARNING]
Protecting the Integrity of LCES is Critical
If bad information or sloppy reasoning gets into the system, it undermines the entire project. It gives opponents ammunition to discredit the work and erodes trust. Maintaining high standards for data and analysis is the first line of defense.
> 

